    +$  private-key    @uwprivatekey
    +$  signature      @uwsignature
    ::
    +|  %kinetics
    ::  $channel: combined sender and receiver identifying data
    ::
    +$  channel
      $:  [our=ship her=ship]
          now=@da
          ::  our data, common to all dyads
          ::
          $:  =our=life
              crypto-core=acru
              =bug
          ==
          ::  her data, specific to this dyad
